In re Resignation of Weinberger.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Weinberger (1995), 74 Ohio St.3d 1206.]

(No. 95-1851 Submitted September 27, 1995 Decided September 28, 1995.)

The resignation as an attorney of Barrett N. Weinberger of Cincinnati, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0043744, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
